subject: Order Ratifying the Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Republic of Poland on the Protection of Classified Information
precis: Order authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the Agreement on the Protection of Classified Information between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Republic of Poland, done at Warsaw on January 16, 2025.
